CBRE is delighted to offer 134-140 Gaffney Street, Coburg North, for lease. 

This is a rare opportunity to rent your own piece of this tightly held northern industrial market! Potential to lease the entire site or separately. Further hardstand space is available for lease on the corner of Mercier Street & Gaffney Street for additional staff or customer parking.

The subject property is strategically located on Gaffney Street in the heart of Coburg North offering great main road exposure for all business types. Good proximity to major arterials including the Metropolitan Ring Road, Tullamarine Freeway & Calder Freeway, furthermore only minutes from Melbourne Airport.

These multi-functional warehouses afford the following features and are available immediately:

WAREHOUSE 1: 134 GAFFNEY STREET
+ Total floor area: 486sqm*
+ Total land area: 630sqm*
+ 8 on-site car spaces
+ Large clear span warehouse space
+ Motorised roller door access

WAREHOUSE 2: 136 GAFFNEY STREET
+ Total floor area: 1,170sqm*
+ Total land area: 1,250sqm*
+ Large clear span warehouse space
+ Refurbished office/showroom
+ Dual roller door access
+ 10 on-site car spaces
+ Industrial 3 Zone (IN3Z)

For further information or to arrange an on-site inspection, please contact the CBRE team.

This 440sqm* office/warehouse on 650sqm* of land is situated in the tightly held industrial hub of Coburg North. This building is perfect for storage with the view to develop (STCA) and build a new headquarters for your business in a thriving City Fringe location.

Located just off Gaffney Street with immediate access onto Bakers Road, Sydney Road and just 11km from Melbourne’s CBD. The property is just metres away from the Lincoln Mills Home maker centre with occupiers such as Bunnings, BCF, Petbarn & Officeworks.

Property Features Include:

-	Total Building Area: 440sqm*
-	Land Area: 650sqm*
-	Development potential (STCA)

-	High clearance

-	Close to CBD

CBRE in conjunction with DGi Properties are pleased to offer you the opportunity to secure this large corner industrial site for sale via Public Auction on Thursday 15th September 2016 at 12:30pm on site.

Situated on a prime corner allotment, the property boasts two street frontages and can be accessed from both Milkman Way and Dairy Drive.

Located just metres from busy Newlands Road, the property holds a premium position within the Newlands Road Estate just 15 kilometres* north of Melbourne's CBD.

- Total building area: 850sqm*
- Total land area: 1,324sqm*
- Large corner allotment with ample on site parking
- 2x container height roller doors
- 3x large cool rooms
- High clearance warehousing
- First floor mezzanine open plan office area
- Excellent northern suburb location

The property offers an outstanding opportunity to purchase in one of Melbourne's highly sought after commercial hubs.

Located at 2 Dairy Drive (Cnr Newlands Road), Coburg North, this newly leased operational car wash and take away cafe has dual access from Newlands Road and Dairy Drive.

Positioned 15km* north of Melbourne's CBD, Queen Victoria Market and 1km* from Sydney Road shopping strip, this property provides great access to major arterials such as City Link.
